name: Latest Request
query:
SELECT rf.name as 'Request Number:Link/Request Form:150',
rf.file_number as 'File Number:Data:150',
rf.full_name as 'Full Name:Read Only:200',
date_of_request as 'Date of Request:Date:100',
DATEDIFF(NOW(),date_of_request) as 'Days Spent:Int:150'
FROM `tabRequest Form` rf  
WHERE DATEDIFF(NOW(),date_of_request) >= 182
GROUP BY rf.file_number;
